# Project Chowky - Monorepo Structure

This is a TypeScript monorepo built with Better-T-Stack using:
- **Turborepo** for monorepo orchestration
- **Bun** as the runtime and package manager
- **Biome** for linting and formatting

## Architecture

- **Frontend**: React + TanStack Router + TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui in [apps/web/](mdc:apps/web/)
- **Backend**: Hono + tRPC + Drizzle ORM + PostgreSQL in [apps/server/](mdc:apps/server/)

## Key Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root package.json with workspace configuration
- [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json) - Turborepo build configuration  
- [biome.json](mdc:biome.json) - Biome linting and formatting rules
- [bts.jsonc](mdc:bts.jsonc) - Better-T-Stack configuration

## Development Commands

- `bun dev` - Start all applications
- `bun dev:web` - Start frontend only
- `bun dev:server` - Start backend only  
- `bun db:push` - Push database schema changes
- `bun check` - Run Biome formatting and linting

## Frontend Structure (apps/web/)

- [apps/web/src/routes/](mdc:apps/web/src/routes/) - TanStack Router file-based routing
- [apps/web/src/components/](mdc:apps/web/src/components/) - Reusable React components
- [apps/web/src/lib/](mdc:apps/web/src/lib/) - Utility functions and configurations

## Backend Structure (apps/server/)

- [apps/server/src/routers/](mdc:apps/server/src/routers/) - tRPC router definitions
- [apps/server/src/db/](mdc:apps/server/src/db/) - Drizzle ORM schema and database utilities
- [apps/server/src/lib/](mdc:apps/server/src/lib/) - Server utilities and configurations
